      <title>Conversor</title>
      <link>https://borhuub.github.io/writeups/conversor/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://borhuub.github.io/writeups/conversor/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;conversor_machine&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://borhuub.github.io/img/conversor/conversor_machine.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;reconocimiento&#34;&gt;Reconocimiento&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;nmap -p- --open -sS --min-rate &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;5000&lt;/span&gt; -vvv -n -Pn 10.129.113.208 -oG ports
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Host discovery disabled &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;-Pn&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;. All addresses will be marked &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;up&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; and scan &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;times&lt;/span&gt; may be slower.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Starting Nmap 7.93 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt; https://nmap.org &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; at 2025-10-25 21:13 CEST
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Initiating SYN Stealth Scan at 21:13
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Scanning 10.129.113.208 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;65535&lt;/span&gt; ports&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Discovered open port 80/tcp on 10.129.113.208
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Discovered open port 22/tcp on 10.129.113.208
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Completed SYN Stealth Scan at 21:13, 10.54s elapsed &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;65535&lt;/span&gt; total ports&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap scan report &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; 10.129.113.208
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Host is up, received user-set &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0.036s latency&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Scanned at 2025-10-25 21:13:37 CEST &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; 11s
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Not shown: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;65533&lt;/span&gt; closed tcp ports &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;reset&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;PORT   STATE SERVICE REASON
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;22/tcp open  ssh     syn-ack ttl &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;63&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;80/tcp open  http    syn-ack ttl &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;63&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Read data files from: /usr/bin/../share/nmap
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; IP address &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; host up&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; scanned in 10.61 seconds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;           Raw packets sent: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;66137&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;2.910MB&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; Rcvd: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;65535&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;2.621MB&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;ports.py ports
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;🔍 Puertos encontrados:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  ➜  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  ➜  &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;80&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;¡Puertos copiados en el portapapeles!
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;nmap -p 20,80 -sCV 10.129.113.208 -oN targeted
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Starting Nmap 7.93 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt; https://nmap.org &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; at 2025-10-25 21:23 CEST
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap scan report &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; 10.129.113.208
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Host is up &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;0.14s latency&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;PORT   STATE  SERVICE  VERSION
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;20/tcp closed ftp-data
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;80/tcp open   http     Apache httpd 2.4.52
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;_http-server-header: Apache/2.4.52 &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Ubuntu&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;_http-title: Did not follow redirect to http://conversor.htb/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Service Info: Host: conversor.htb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Service detection performed. Please report any incorrect results at https://nmap.org/submit/ .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Nmap &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; IP address &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; host up&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; scanned in 10.34 seconds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;enumeración-web&#34;&gt;Enumeración web&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Una vez entramos a la web vemos que tenemos un panel de login, pero podemos registrarnos, así que nos registramos y entramos a la página web.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
